      <element xsi:type="archimate:CourseOfAction" name="Alerts trigger model AI automation on client needs and solution gaps" id="id-43d54ab36d6a4e889c7270eb5e20173b">
        <documentation>Initiative planned for May that can automate 50% - “trigger model” AI learning tool that can proactively pre-empt what clients will want or use. They’ve defined triggers already with the alerts needed. Sales enablement and dev teams. &#xD;
Heavily-dependent on data&#xD;
Sector Payments Pulse just released so now we can get views into their flows. &#xD;
&#xD;
With the trigger model, there is potential for R3-12mil increased contribution.</documentation>
      </element>
