            <child xsi:type="archimate:Note" id="id-3d4dac1fe1fd4de1b9c68d64ceab6a38" textAlignment="1">
              <bounds x="12" y="12" width="601" height="189"/>
              <content>Amendment Scenarios:&#xD;
1. Pre-settlement amendment &#xD;
2. Pre-settlement cancellations&#xD;
3. Partial early withdrawals (close deal (terminationa + new deal) (early rollover?)&#xD;
3. Full early withdrawal (close deal)&#xD;
4. Rate changes (call/notice only) - allow for term linked to repo/zaronia rate?&#xD;
5. SSI changes, contact details, etc. - impact one deposit or many (???) Mandates could change.&#xD;
6. Maturity Instruction changes&#xD;
7. Bank deal corrections / reversals&#xD;
8. Late client funding payment (past due) - Stu to come back on this&#xD;
&#xD;
On dealer dashboard - show quotes that need to be actioned before the end of the day. </content>
            </child>
