                <bounds x="720" y="288" width="456" height="76"/>
                <content>Payment Hierarchy - doesn't cater for crossborder YET, but will in future. &#xD;
Order Allocation - Payment / Smart Routing - Derivation service&#xD;
Correspondent Bank is determined in FX payment rail. But can ask for preferred correspondent.</content>
              </child>
