                <bounds x="1434" y="18" width="145" height="84"/>
                <content>In future, should fees or charges be required, the payment order would be processed after placing the deposit in the market. </content>
              </child>
              <child xsi:type="archimate:Note" id="id-db5534f4a5d14a05a4723f3d06cbbae4" textAlignment="1">
                <bounds x="120" y="95" width="151" height="37"/>
                <content>Cut off times and currency non business days</content>
              </child>
              <child xsi:type="archimate:Note" id="id-dd7ed4c787a245a9ad4577773c35f196" textAlignment="1">
                <bounds x="1152" y="20" width="121" height="37"/>
                <content>How do we manage unreconciled items? </content>
              </child>
