                <bounds x="1440" y="109" width="157" height="73"/>
                <content>Chameleon TS accounts feed to RADA&#xD;
&#xD;
Create this view on Finxact.</content>
              </child>
              <child xsi:type="archimate:Note" id="id-c33fd2f3344e4aafa613256ea2eeaa14" textAlignment="1">
                <bounds x="355" y="7" width="121" height="64"/>
                <content>future-dated for currency? what about rate changes? </content>
              </child>
