              </child>
            </child>
            <child xsi:type="archimate:Note" id="id-873a2031a5a84b0b911cdb57eacb030c" textAlignment="1">
              <bounds x="888" y="198" width="229" height="91"/>
              <content>To be determined whether internal interest postings to be executed on receiving events or kicked-off as part of end-of-day batch processes (which are generally accepted practice).</content>
            </child>
            <child xsi:type="archimate:Note" id="id-33930114baf34b3881e8503dbeeeee4a" textAlignment="1">
              <bounds x="840" y="48" width="108" height="72"/>
              <content>confirm the interest convention used for interest accrual</content>
            </child>
