          <child xsi:type="archimate:Note" id="id-b41fa10dc76743e8bba27657e0221f9d" textAlignment="1">
            <bounds x="-43" y="228" width="180" height="108"/>
            <content>All the source systems kick off their own end of day processes. &#xD;
&#xD;
JSE sends an EOD rate and that kicks off an MDP process, which triggers the Calypso end of day. </content>
          </child>
          <child xsi:type="archimate:DiagramObject" id="id-b0c5fccd58ec4b43a1423d4d26798f7e" archimateElement="id-c00bf20effe849928620746f32b3c641">
