            <child xsi:type="archimate:Note" id="id-33c7e6a7ea2a4392b08345a09d63d4fe" textAlignment="1">
              <bounds x="60" y="552" width="121" height="61"/>
              <content>e.g. reverse factoring for company, new solution and client - sharing of limited information, make sure you have NDA, then get financials, suppliers, terms of trade in their operations. Collate and run pricing model, tweak margins on facilities, building out solution, collaborate on structure. Client shows interest and then we start onboarding to platforms, initiate KYC process, credit approvals, etc. (legals require external engagements - incurs costs)</content>
            </child>
          </child>
